==English==

===Etymology===
Came from the minstrel show song "Jump ''Jim Crow''", written in 1828 by Thomas D. Rice, the originator of [[blackface]] performance.

===Proper noun===
'''Jim Crow laws'''

#[[Discrimination]] against [[African American]]s.

'''Jim Crow'''

# A generic name for the Negro.POOP

